  "title": "AB03 - Sales Executive (F&B ) - Class 3",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sales Executive (F&B ) - Class 3</strong></p><p>Working days & hours: 5days, Mon - Fri 9:45am - 6pm</p><p>Location: Redhill</p><p>Salary: Basic $3100 - $3300</p><p><strong>Job scopes:</strong></p><ul><li>Drive sales growth and manage key accounts.</li><li>Identify and unlock new business opportunities with smart strategies.</li><li>Build and maintain strong, lasting customer relationships.</li><li>Plan and execute sales campaigns to achieve targets.</li><li>Meet and exceed sales targets through proactive planning and execution.</li><li>Represent the company at events, trade shows, and client meetings.</li><li>Conduct market research to understand trends and customer needs.</li><li>Prepare sales reports and forecasts for management.</li><li>Collaborate with the marketing team on promotional activities.</li><li>Negotiate contracts and close deals to maximize revenue.</li><li>Monitor competitor activities and recommend strategic actions.</li><li>Provide excellent after-sales support to ensure customer satisfaction.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 3 years’ experience in food industry sales (selling to food producers is a plus)</li><li>Valid Class 3 driver’s license.</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
